issue_comments.body:
@arrbee You are correct. I had thought, from what you wrote, that I made a lot of issues for the org.  I posted too soon.  

I since checked which issues I created and confirmed it was only one for you.  As you can imagine, I don't want to annoy people.  There's a fine line between explaining where the PR comes from and actually saying automated.  People respond a lot more nicely if I don't explicitly say I generated the issue from the command-line.  In any case, I follow up on every issue I create.  I'm more of a cyborg.

Anyhow, I'll make a PR now, if you'd like that.
